name: Spiderbear Torment #1
description:
The Bear-Lizard is on a murder spree and Spider Bear is here to stop him. In the exchange, the Bear-Lizard poisons Spider Bear and throws him off a building. Can Spider Bear survive the deadly toxin and discover the truth behind Bear-Lizards killings?

Now you can collect this fine commemorative Token of TORMENT #1 Todd McBearlins famous entry to the Spider Bear Franchise
